---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import QuickSummary from '../components/QuickSummary.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Events" 
  description="VS daily focus schedule, best Arms Race chest strategy, and Alliance Trial tips for Last War: Survival mid-game players."
>
  <h1>Events</h1>

  <QuickSummary>
    <p>Events are your most consistent source of progress. Treat VS and Arms Race as non-negotiable daily/weekly activities.</p>
  </QuickSummary>

  <h2>VS (Victory Showdown) Daily Focus</h2>
  <p>Each day has a primary focus. Align your spending and participation with the daily theme for maximum efficiency.</p>

  <div class="table-wrapper">
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Day</th><th>Primary Focus</th><th>Notes</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Monday</td><td>Hero Shards / Recruitment</td><td>Good day to use tickets and alliance store shards</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Tuesday</td><td>Gear &amp; Enhancement</td><td>Ore and component events often align</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Wednesday</td><td>Research / Tech</td><td>Push research speed and academy</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Thursday</td><td>Troops &amp; Training</td><td>Train the type you’re currently pushing</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Friday</td><td>Resources / Gathering</td><td>Load marches and elite runs</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Saturday</td><td>PvP / Arena focused</td><td>Stronger rally windows, use best squads</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Sunday</td><td>General / Cleanup</td><td>Catch up on missed chests and dailies</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <h2>Arms Race Chest Strategy (High Value)</h2>
  
  <QuickSummary>
    <p><strong>Save your big stamina and high-tier chests for the final 3–4 hours.</strong> This is when alliance gift multipliers and personal milestone rewards are at their strongest.</p>
  </QuickSummary>

  <p>The single biggest mistake mid-game players make is popping every chest as soon as they earn it.</p>

  <div class="table-wrapper">
    <table>
      <thead><tr><th>Phase</th><th>What You Should Do</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Early/Mid Event</td><td>Complete daily missions with smaller/medium chests. Save legendary and high-stamina chests.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Last 3–4 Hours</td><td>Pop your saved high-value chests. Coordinate with alliance for maximum gift points.</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Final Hour</td><td>Focus on personal milestone chests if you're close. Alliance gifts are usually maxed by now.</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <h2>Alliance Trial</h2>
  <p>Runs twice per week in most servers. This is one of the best sources of alliance ranking points and individual rewards.</p>
  <ul class="text-sm">
    <li>Bring your strongest available squad</li>
    <li>Focus fire on the alliance-designated main target</li>
    <li>Many alliances create a dedicated voice/text channel for the event so everyone rallies the same boss</li>
  </ul>

  <p class="text-sm text-[#8a96b0] mt-2">Pro tip: If your alliance is small or disorganized, you can still get excellent personal rewards by just showing up with your best squad and following whatever target the stronger players are hitting.</p>
</Layout>